  <md:abstract>By the end of this section, you will be able to:
<list>
<item>Explain the process of measurement</item>
<item>Identify the three basic parts of a quantity</item>
<item>Describe the properties and units of length, mass, volume, density, temperature, and time</item>
<item>Perform basic unit calculations and conversions in the metric and other unit systems</item>
</list></md:abstract>
  <md:language>en</md:language>
